verbose_text: Several open-chain chelators such as hydroxyaromatic diamines like N, N '-di (2-hydroxybenzyl) ethylenediamine-N, N '-diacetic acid (HBED), pyridoxylethylenediamines such as N, N '-dipyridoxyethylenediamine-N, N '-diacetic acid (PLED), mono- and bifunctional open chain chelators based on [tris (aminomethyl) ethane] (TAME) formed complexes with improved stability XREF_BIBR.
